message.entry: CustomFloat is not supported for HDL/HLS code generation.
Input datatype {0} is not supported for creating CustomFloat object.
Floating-point type must be specified as ''double'', ''single'', ''half'', or of CustomFloat class.
Word length of CustomFloat object must be equal to the word length of the object being cast.
Datatype {0} not supported for typecasting to a CustomFloat object.
Exponent length must be less than 31.
Real and Imag of complex CustomFloat object must have same dimension.
Norm type not supported for CustomFloat objects.
Assignment of complex CustomFloat object to non-complex CustomFloat object is not supported.
For CustomFloat objects, cat/horzcat/vertcat only supports up to 2D array.
Method {0} is undefined for complex number of CustomFloat type.
